## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="460af-103">此类实现<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-103">This class implements the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> class.</span></span>  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="460af-104">从.NET Framework 2.0 开始，我们建议你创建<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>实例使用<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法和<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings>类以利用新功能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-104">Starting with the .NET Framework 2.0, we recommend that you create <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instances by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings> class to take advantage of new functionality.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-105">`XmlTextWriter` 维护对应的当前元素堆栈中定义的所有命名空间的命名空间堆栈。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-105">`XmlTextWriter` maintains a namespace stack corresponding to all the namespaces defined in the current element stack.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-106">使用`XmlTextWriter`可以手动声明命名空间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-106">Using `XmlTextWriter` you can declare namespaces manually.</span></span>  

```  
w.WriteStartElement("root");  
w.WriteAttributeString("xmlns", "x", null, "urn:1");  
 w.WriteStartElement("item","urn:1");  
 w.WriteEndElement();  
 w.WriteStartElement("item","urn:1");  
 w.WriteEndElement();  
w.WriteEndElement();  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-107">上面的 C# 代码生成以下输出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-107">The above C# code produces the following output.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-108">`XmlTextWriter` 提升到要避免使其重复上两个子元素的根元素的命名空间声明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-108">`XmlTextWriter` promotes the namespace declaration to the root element to avoid having it duplicated on the two child elements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-109">子元素选取从命名空间声明的前缀。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-109">The child elements pick up the prefix from the namespace declaration.</span></span>  

```  
<root xmlns:x="urn:1">  
 <x:item/>  
 <x:item/>  
</x:root>  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-110">`XmlTextWriter` 此外允许你重写当前命名空间声明。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-110">`XmlTextWriter` also allows you to override the current namespace declaration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-111">在下面的示例中，命名空间 URI"123"已由"abc"要生成的 XML 元素`<x:node xmlns:x="abc"/>`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-111">In the following example, the namespace URI "123" is overridden by "abc" to produce the XML element `<x:node xmlns:x="abc"/>`.</span></span>  

```  
w.WriteStartElement("x","node","123");  
w.WriteAttributeString("xmlns","x",null,"abc");  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-112">通过使用需要作为自变量的前缀的写入方法还可以指定的前缀，以使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-112">By using the write methods that take a prefix as an argument you can also specify which prefix to use.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-113">在下面的示例中，两个不同的前缀映射到相同的命名空间 URI 以产生的 XML 文本`<x:root xmlns:x="urn:1"><y:item xmlns:y="urn:1"/></x:root>`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-113">In the following example, two different prefixes are mapped to the same namespace URI to produce the XML text `<x:root xmlns:x="urn:1"><y:item xmlns:y="urn:1"/></x:root>`.</span></span>  

```  
XmlTextWriter w = new XmlTextWriter(Console.Out);  
w.WriteStartElement("x","root","urn:1");  
 w.WriteStartElement("y","item","urn:1");  
 w.WriteEndElement();  
w.WriteEndElement();  
w.Close();  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-114">如果有多个命名空间声明将不同的前缀映射到相同的命名空间 URI，`XmlTextWriter`向后遍历的命名空间声明堆栈并选取最近一个命名空间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-114">If there are multiple namespace declarations mapping different prefixes to the same namespace URI, `XmlTextWriter` walks the stack of namespace declarations backwards and picks the closest one.</span></span>  

```  
XmlTextWriter w = new XmlTextWriter(Console.Out);  
w.Formatting = Formatting.Indented;  
w.WriteStartElement("x","root","urn:1");  
w.WriteStartElement("y","item","urn:1");  
w.WriteAttributeString("attr","urn:1","123");  
w.WriteEndElement();  
w.WriteEndElement();  
w.Close();  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-115">在上面的 C# 示例，因为`WriteAttributeString`调用未指定前缀，编写器使用推送到命名空间堆栈上的最后一个前缀，并生成下面的 XML:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-115">In the above C# example, because the `WriteAttributeString` call does not specify a prefix, the writer uses the last prefix pushed onto the namespace stack, and produces the following XML:</span></span>  

```  
<x:root xmlns:x="urn:1">  
 <y:item y:attr="123" xmlns:y="urn:1" />  
</x:root>  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-116">如果发生命名空间冲突，`XmlTextWriter`解析它们通过生成的备用前缀。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-116">If namespace conflicts occur, `XmlTextWriter` resolves them by generating alternate prefixes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-117">例如，如果属性和元素具有相同前缀但不同的命名空间，`XmlWriter`生成的属性的备用前缀。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-117">For example, if an attribute and element have the same prefix but different namespaces, `XmlWriter` generates an alternate prefix for the attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-118">生成的前缀命名`n{i}`其中`i`是从 1 开始的数字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-118">The generated prefixes are named `n{i}` where `i` is a number beginning at 1.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-119">编号重置为 1。 对于每个元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-119">The number is reset to 1 for each element.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-120">命名空间 URI 与关联的属性必须具有的前缀 （默认值特性不适用于命名空间）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-120">Attributes which are associated with a namespace URI must have a prefix (default namespaces do not apply to attributes).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-121">这符合 XML 建议中的 W3C 命名空间的第 5.2 节。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-121">This conforms to section 5.2 of the W3C Namespaces in XML recommendation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-122">如果属性引用的命名空间 URI，但未指定前缀，则编写器将生成该属性的前缀。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-122">If an attribute references a namespace URI, but does not specify a prefix, the writer generates a prefix for the attribute.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-123">当编写空元素，额外的空间之间添加标记名称和结束标记，例如`<item />`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-123">When writing an empty element, an additional space is added between tag name and the closing tag, for example `<item />`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-124">这提供了与较旧的浏览器兼容性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-124">This provides compatibility with older browsers.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-125">当`String`作为方法参数，使用`null`和`String.Empty`是等效的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-125">When a `String` is used as method parameter, `null` and `String.Empty` are equivalent.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-126">`String.Empty` 遵循 W3C 规则。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-126">`String.Empty` follows the W3C rules.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-127">若要编写强类型化的数据，使用<xref:System.Xml.XmlConvert>类将数据类型转换为字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-127">To write strongly typed data, use the <xref:System.Xml.XmlConvert> class to convert data types to string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-128">例如，下面的 C# 代码将转换中的数据`Double`到`String`编写元素和`<price>19.95</price>`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-128">For example, the following C# code converts the data from `Double` to `String` and writes the element `<price>19.95</price>`.</span></span>  

```  
Double price = 19.95;  
writer.WriteElementString("price", XmlConvert.ToString(price));  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-129">`XmlTextWriter` 不会检查以下：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-129">`XmlTextWriter` does not check for the following:</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="460af-130">属性和元素名称中的无效字符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-130">Invalid characters in attribute and element names.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="460af-131">不符合指定的编码的 Unicode 字符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-131">Unicode characters that do not fit the specified encoding.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-132">如果指定的编码，不能容纳的 Unicode 字符`XmlTextWriter`未转义的 Unicode 字符到字符实体。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-132">If the Unicode characters do not fit the specified encoding, the `XmlTextWriter` does not escape the Unicode characters into character entities.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="460af-133">重复的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-133">Duplicate attributes.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="460af-134">DOCTYPE 公共标识符或系统标识符中的字符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-134">Characters in the DOCTYPE public identifier or system identifier.</span></span>  

## <a name="security-considerations"></a><span data-ttu-id="460af-135">安全注意事项</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-135">Security Considerations</span></span>  
 <span data-ttu-id="460af-136">以下各项是需要时使用，请考虑事项<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter>类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-136">The following items are things to consider when working with the <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> class.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="460af-137">引发的异常<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter>可能会泄漏你不希望的路径信息冒泡由应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-137">Exceptions thrown by the <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> can disclose path information that you do not want bubbled up to the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-138">应用程序必须捕获异常并进行相应的处理。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-138">Your applications must catch exceptions and process them appropriately.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="460af-139">在将 <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> 传递给另一个应用程序时，基础流会公开给该应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-139">When you pass the <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> to another application the underlying stream is exposed to that application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-140">如果需要将 <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> 传递给不完全可信的应用程序，应使用通过 <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> 方法创建的 <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A> 对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-140">If you need to pass the <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> to a semi-trusted application, you should use an <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> object created by the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A> method instead.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="460af-141"><xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter>不会验证传递给任何数据<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.WriteDocType%2A>或<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.WriteRaw%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-141">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter> does not validate any data that is passed to the <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.WriteDocType%2A> or <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.WriteRaw%2A> methods.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-142">你不应将任意数据传递给这些方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-142">You should not pass arbitrary data to these methods.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="460af-143">如果更改默认设置，则不能保证生成的输出是格式良好的 XML 数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-143">If the default settings are changed, there is no guarantee that the generated output is well-formed XML data.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="460af-144">不接受支持组件，如<xref:System.Text.Encoding>中不受信任的源对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-144">Do not accept supporting components, such as an <xref:System.Text.Encoding> object, from an untrusted source.</span></span>



## Remarks  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="460af-188">从.NET Framework 2.0 开始，我们建议你创建<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>实例使用<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法和<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings>类以利用新功能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-188">Starting with the .NET Framework 2.0, we recommend that you create <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instances by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter.Create%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriterSettings> class to take advantage of new functionality.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-189">如果`Indented`选项设置、 子元素缩进使用<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.Indentation%2A>和<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.IndentChar%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-189">If the `Indented` option is set, child elements are indented using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.Indentation%2A> and <xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.IndentChar%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-190">仅元素内容将缩进。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-190">Only element content is indented.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-191">下面的 C# 代码写出包括混合的内容的 HTML 元素：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-191">The following C# code writes out HTML elements including mixed content:</span></span>  

```  
XmlTextWriter w = new XmlTextWriter(Console.Out);   
 w.Formatting = Formatting.Indented;   
 w.WriteStartElement("ol");   
 w.WriteStartElement("li");   
 w.WriteString("The big "); // This means "li" now has a mixed content model.  
 w.WriteElementString("b", "E");   
 w.WriteElementString("i", "lephant");   
 w.WriteString(" walks slowly.");   
 w.WriteEndElement();   
 w.WriteEndElement();  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-192">上面的代码生成以下输出：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-192">The above code produces the following output:</span></span>  

```  
<ol>   
  <li>The big <b>E</b><i>lephant</i> walks slowly.</li>   
</ol>  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="460af-193">这在 HTML 中查看时不出现空白粗体和斜体元素之间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-193">When this is viewed in HTML no white space appears between the bold and italic elements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-194">事实上，在此示例中，如果这些元素之间添加缩进"象"一词将是不正确地断开。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-194">In fact, in this example, if indenting was added between these elements the word "Elephant" would be incorrectly broken.</span></span>  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="460af-195">写入内容，不包括任何文本`String.Empty`将该元素放入混合内容的模式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-195">Writing any text content, excluding `String.Empty` puts that element into mixed content mode.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-196">子元素不会继承此"混合"模式状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-196">Child elements do not inherit this "mixed" mode status.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-197">"混合"元素的子元素进行缩进，除非它是还包含"混合"的内容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-197">A child element of a "mixed" element does indenting, unless it is also contains "mixed" content.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="460af-198">元素内容 (http://www.w3.org/TR/1998/REC-xml-19980210#sec-element-content)和混合内容 (http://www.w3.org/TR/1998/REC-xml-19980210#sec-mixed-content)根据这些术语的 XML 1.0 定义定义。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="460af-198">Element content (http://www.w3.org/TR/1998/REC-xml-19980210#sec-element-content) and mixed content (http://www.w3.org/TR/1998/REC-xml-19980210#sec-mixed-content) are defined according to the XML 1.0 definitions of these terms.</span></span>  



